The '''Andoan marsh lizard''' was a giant predator native to the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ando/Legends|Ando]]. The creature inhabited Ando's coastal swamps, and had a dull brown scaly hide. Possessing a flat head with eyes angled at forty-five degrees, the Andoan marsh lizard could see above the water when submerged. Andoan marsh lizards had four legs; the front two terminated in sharp claws, while the rear two were flippers used from propulsion. Growing to a size of four and half [[Meter/Legends|meters]] long, the creature also had a short flat tail that could be used as a third flipper when swimming and could also be used as a rudder to turn in water.<ref name="Ando">{{JournalCite|11|The Ando Project}}</ref>

